Web Developer in Nepal WordPress Developer in Nepal Website Design

Hi, I am Alwin Kansakar, a freelancing Web Developer / WordPress developer based in Kathmandu, Nepal. I have a diverse set of skills, ranging from design all the way to PHP, custom WordPress Theme Development. Also , I have strong engineering professional skilled in WordPress, Search Engine Optimization (SEO), PHP, SQL, Bootstrap, HTML 5 and CSS 3.

Web Developer in Nepal WordPress Developer in Nepal Website Design

Hence , first half of my work experience is working as WP Developer in top IT agency . The scope of my work is a large part of the Theme Development and front end: HTML/CSS/JS, coding layouts.

But many times I work with some back end applications written in PHP / MySQL.

wp:postmeta.wp:meta_value: I excel at custom front end design and custom WordPress Theme development.

My goal would be to develop a user friendly design that communicates with your audience which encourages recursive visits and referrals via social media and other channels. Taking advantage of these resources and holding true to current and effective web practices, my web design and development solutions are customized to help you achieve your digital marketing goals.

A CMS, or content management system, is a tool that allows you manage the content of your website independently. WordPress is flexible, highly customizable, super user-friendly, and is a great content management system (CMS). You can use it business websites, and even e-commerce. I am a skilled developers that can bring your site up to date and add that custom touch you always wanted.

Search engine optimization services are unique to the industry with verifiable results. Our SEO team has a track record of improving the authority of a website with strategic on- and offsite Google marketing techniques. Engaging content is pivotal and our experts can spread your unique online voice across your blog, website pages, social media platforms and so much more.
